The Chrome extension URL Blocker helps to easily block any unwanted websites in Google's Chrome browser.

This extension is available for those who specifically want to prevent certain URLs from being called up within Google's Chrome browser. The settings can be used to define URLs or URL patterns using regular expressions that are not required to be called in the browser:
